What kind of acid trip is this shit!!!!? Not only are the characters severe drug addicts, 
the author must have been tripping as hell when he/she made this!!?
I wish someone would translate this. I wanna know what's happening! Why do they switch genders? Why does one of them get a pouch?
What the fuck is happening in this story? Girls in holes, shit everywhere, eating shit everywhere, random old guy, curry, then everyone's anatomy gets fucked. What the fuck did i just look at????
